#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#: _guides/transaction.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using transactions in Quarkus"
msgstr "Uso de transaĂ§Ă”es no Quarkus"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _guides/transaction.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `quarkus-narayana-jta` extension provides a Transaction Manager that coordinates and expose transactions to your applications as described in the link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/transactions/[Jakarta Transactions] specification, formerly known as Java Transaction API (JTA)."
msgstr "A extensĂŁo `quarkus-narayana-jta` fornece um Transaction Manager que coordena e expĂ”e as transaĂ§Ă”es aos seus aplicativos, conforme descrito na especificaĂ§ĂŁo link:https://jakarta.ee/specifications/transactions/[Jakarta Transactions] , anteriormente conhecida como Java Transaction API (JTA)."

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/transaction.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "When discussing Quarkus transactions, this guide refers to Jakarta Transactions transaction style and uses only the term _transaction_ to address them."
msgstr "Ao discutir as transaĂ§Ă”es do Quarkus, este guia se refere ao estilo de transaĂ§ĂŁo do Jakarta Transactions e usa apenas o termo _transaĂ§ĂŁo_ para abordĂĄ-las."

#. type: Plain text
#: _guides/transaction.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Also, Quarkus does not support distributed transactions.\n"
"This means that models that propagate transaction context, such as link:https://download.oracle.com/otndocs/jcp/7309-jts-1.0-spec-oth-JSpec/[Java Transaction Service] (JTS), REST-AT, WS-Atomic Transaction, and others, are not supported by the `narayana-jta` extension."
msgstr "AlĂ©m disso, o Quarkus nĂŁo oferece suporte a transaĂ§Ă”es distribuĂ­das. Isso significa que os modelos que propagam o contexto da transaĂ§ĂŁo, como link:https://download.oracle.com/otndocs/jcp/7309-jts-1.0-spec-oth-JSpec/[Java Transaction Service] (JTS), REST-AT, WS-Atomic Transaction e outros, nĂŁo sĂŁo compatĂ­veis com a extensĂŁo `narayana-jta` ."

#. type: Title =
#: _guides/transaction.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "Setting it up"
msgstr "ConfiguraĂ§ĂŁo"

#. type: Plain text
